\n<Sonoda Kohei>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]「.........」

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF] Don't be so cautious... I
just have something to talk about.

\n<Sonoda Kohei>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F] ......Talk? What, did you
finally feel like helping out?

\n<Kino>.........Yeah, I guess it's fine to side with you.
However, there are conditions.

\n<Sonoda Kohei>Conditions? Well, I guess I'll hear them out for
now...

Kino stood up straight and looked straight into my
eyes.

\n<Kino>......What is the important secret that Sonoda-
san holds? Presenting that information is a
condition.

\n<Sonoda Kohei>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F] ...Isn't that a bit one-
sided? Sorry, but I can't easily talk about it.

\n<Kino>Well, I guess that's true... There's a possibility
that I might snitch, after all.

\n<Sonoda Kohei>No, I trust you on that. I know Kino isn't the
kind of person to do something like that.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF] W-What's with that... If
that's the case, then why...

\n<Sonoda Kohei>There's one thing I want to ask Kino. If you
answer honestly, I'll reveal the information.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF] ...Is that really okay? If
it's just that much...

This time, I straightened my posture and looked
directly into Kino's eyes.

\n<Sonoda Kohei>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F] ......The question is simple.
What is the real reason for Kino siding with Udo?

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF] ...D-Didn't I already tell
you? It's because I'm being blackmailed with
evidence of my involvement with him...

\n<Sonoda Kohei>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F] Certainly, that might be true.
But didn't you phrase it in a way that implies
there's another reason?

\n<Sonoda Kohei>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F] There might be a clue to
finding a solution by talking, and if Kino wishes
for it, I will never reveal it.

\n<Sonoda Kohei>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F] Kino... I still intend to be
your manager. If there's something you can't solve
on your own... please, rely on me.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF] ...You won't tell anyone,
right...?

\n<Sonoda Kohei>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F] I will absolutely not tell
anyone.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF] From someone else's
perspective, it's really a trivial matter... but
do you never laugh...?

\n<Sonoda Kohei>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F] I don't laugh, and there's
nothing trivial about it...

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF] I see... That's right. You're
that kind of person...

Kino lowered \F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]their head and
\r[kept silent. After a moment of deep thought,
\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]they finally opened
\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]their mouth.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF] It's the first time... I've
experienced it...

\n<Sonoda Kohei>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F] For the first time... what do
you mean?

\n<Kino>That's why... I came for the first time! With Udo,
during sex!

\n<Sonoda Kohei>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F] ...Um... Was there nothing
before that? I mean...

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF] Well... I've had some light
orgasms before. But that kind of climax experience
was the first time for me...

\n<Kino>Until now, I've never felt satisfied even when I
masturbated alone... I always thought it was
because there was something wrong with my body...

\n<Sonoda Kohei>I see... So, you became dependent on your sexual
encounters with Udo, is that what you're saying?
\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF] Yeah... To put it simply...

\n<Sonoda Kohei>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F] (Is it a mental issue...? It
seems like there's no problem with your body...)

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF] You must be disgusted, right?
That I betrayed Neon for such a reason? Honestly,
I feel pathetic myself... And I'm sorry to
everyone...

\n<Sonoda Kohei>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F] 'Well, the troubles that one
person carries may seem trivial to others... but
to the person themselves, even something light can
feel heavy.'

\n<Sonoda Kohei>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F] It must have been tough... I'm
sorry for not noticing...

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF] Sonoda-san, you didn't do
anything wrong... Ugh, ughhh...

Kino put both hands on her face and collapsed in
tears. Unable to find the right words to say, I
could only stay silent and wait for her to stop
crying...

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF] Haa... I cried, I cried...
It's been years since I last cried...

\n<Sonoda Kohei>It's regrettable that I didn't have a camera. It
was a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity to hold onto
a weakness of hers...

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF] This damn perverted bastard
with a small, pathetic dick...

\n<Sonoda Kohei>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F] Stop with the small dick... It
hurts boys, you know...

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF] Hahaha... However, I did
something regrettable.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF] I missed the first and last
chance to corrupt Kino-chan, you know? If I had
gently embraced her or something, she would have
easily fallen for me...
\n<Sonoda Kohei>Seriously... Kino-chan is easy.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF] You're such a wimp! Well...
that aside.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF] ......I can't understand
something.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF] Not only did you expose my
secret, but you also made me show my crying
face...

\n<Sonoda Kohei>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F] Hey, don't say things that
sound bad. I didn't really expose anything, right?

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF] ......It's okay to keep this
a secret, right?
Kino stands up with a bewitching smile.
